# ChromaDB / vector store data — baked into Docker image for Railway.
# These ARE committed so the Docker build has the pre-populated catalog.
# Only exclude the gitkeep placeholder (it's replaced by real files).
# data/chroma_db/*/     <-- intentionally NOT excluded
# data/*.db             <-- intentionally NOT excluded for Railway Docker
# Uncomment the lines below if you want to exclude them again locally:
# data/chroma_db/*/
# !data/chroma_db/.gitkeep
# data/*.db

